Before running install file please install Dependencies
you must install aria2 bc pm-utils wget mpg123 
for debian base distributions :  debian , ubuntu , mint , ...
sudo apt-get install aria2  wget  pm-utils  bc mpg123
for fedora:
sudo yum install aria2  wget  pm-utils  bc mpg123
for arch:
sudo pacman -S aria2  wget  pm-utils  bc mpg123  
